  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-01 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This synthetic adversarial package embeds W-EP-01: the bound Claim node carries a thorough prose description referencing supporting validation studies but lacks a structured prov:wasDerivedFrom link to any Evidence node, rendering the claim structurally unsupported despite appearing credible on prose review.",
