      "description": "Particle image velocimetry measurements acquired at 5 operating points compared against CFD velocity predictions. Mean absolute error across measurement planes: 6.2% of peak velocity. GCI-based discretization uncertainty: 3.8%.",
      "wasDerivedFrom": "https://uofa.net/synth/evidence/piv-dataset-fda-pump-2023"
    },
    {
