      "name": "Bench hemolysis index comparison — 5 operating points",
      "description": "Normalized index of hemolysis measured via modified ASTM F1841 protocol at 5 target operating conditions. CFD predictions within 28–34% of measured NIH values; all predictions conservative (over-predict hemolysis). Monte Carlo 95th-percentile bound remains below 0.01 g/100 L threshold.",
      "wasDerivedFrom": "https://uofa.net/synth/evidence/hemolysis-bench-dataset-2023"
