    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 credibility factors. Seven factors were assessed; six were flagged as epistemic gaps at MRL 5. The bound Claim (https://uofa.net/synth/claim/vad-hemolysis-model-adequate) documents model adequacy with reference to inter-laboratory round-robin studies and Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification, and the validation results demonstrate conservative hemolysis predictions across all five operating points. On the basis of the prose evidence summarised in the Claim and the two ValidationResult nodes, the package is accepted for submission. The structured derivation chain between the Claim and underlying Evidence nodes was not independently verified by the automated credibility checker.",
